name: Rotten Papers.001 (House & Jazz)
description: Rotten Papers is a series that I respons to anything that I heard. Now, this series is about House & Jazz music, mentioned Theo Parrish, John Coltrane, and Miles Davis in this artwork because I really into them, and I visualized some shape when I heard their music. It's a pleasure to draw with their music in my ears. Rotten Papers will be going to 002, based on a music that I heard the day I draw it.
